## 4. Engine Initialization

Your code uses a **two-phase architecture** for the RAILGUN engine. Here's exactly what happens:

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant UI as React App
    participant Hook as usePrivateWallet
    participant Engine as engine.ts
    participant WASM as RAILGUN WASM
    participant IDB as IndexedDB
    participant RPC as Arbitrum RPC
    participant Supabase as Supabase

    Note over UI,Supabase: Phase 1: Engine Boot (no network)
    Hook->>Engine: ensureEngineStarted()
    Engine->>Engine: Dynamic import @railgun-community/wallet
    Engine->>Engine: Dynamic import @railgun-community/shared-models
    Engine->>WASM: Load WASM binary
    Engine->>IDB: Open 'monaris-railgun-artifacts' DB (v4)
    Engine->>Engine: Create artifact store (get/store/exists callbacks)
    Engine->>WASM: startRailgunEngine(walletSource, db, config)
    Note over Engine: Status: 'initializing' → 'loading-artifacts'
    Engine-->>Hook: Engine booted (~2-4 seconds)

    Note over UI,Supabase: Phase 2: Wallet import (must happen BEFORE provider)
    Hook->>Hook: Sign "Monaris Private Wallet Derivation v1"
    Hook->>Hook: keccak256(signature) → entropy → BIP39 mnemonic
    Hook->>Engine: createRailgunWallet(password, mnemonic, {})
    Engine->>WASM: Import wallet with viewing key
    Engine-->>Hook: { walletId, railgunAddress: "0zk..." }
    Hook->>Supabase: Persist encrypted blob (AES-GCM) [fire and forget]

    Note over UI,Supabase: Phase 3: Load provider + quicksync
    Hook->>Engine: loadProviderAndSync()
    Engine->>RPC: Connect to Arbitrum RPC (with retries)
    Engine->>WASM: loadProvider(chain, [rpcUrl])
    Note over WASM: Quicksync: download Merkle tree updates
    WASM->>RPC: Scan for UTXOs matching this wallet's viewing key
    Note over Engine: Status: 'syncing' → 'ready'

    Note over UI,Supabase: Phase 4: POI refresh
    Hook->>Engine: refreshPOIsForWallet(walletId)
    Engine->>WASM: Generate POI proofs for ShieldPending UTXOs
    WASM->>RPC: Submit POI proofs to aggregator
    Note over Engine: ShieldPending funds → Spendable
```

### Key code paths:

| Phase | File | Function | What it does |
|---|---|---|---|
| 1a | [engine.ts](file:///Users/adityakumar/Library/Mobile%20Documents/com~apple~CloudDocs/monaris-app/src/lib/privacy/engine.ts#L211-L357) | [doEngineStart()](file:///Users/adityakumar/Library/Mobile%20Documents/com~apple~CloudDocs/monaris-app/src/lib/privacy/engine.ts#211-358) | Boots WASM, opens IndexedDB, creates artifact store |
| 1b | [engine.ts](file:///Users/adityakumar/Library/Mobile%20Documents/com~apple~CloudDocs/monaris-app/src/lib/privacy/engine.ts#L82-L176) | [ensureProverInitialized()](file:///Users/adityakumar/Library/Mobile%20Documents/com~apple~CloudDocs/monaris-app/src/lib/privacy/engine.ts#82-177) | Loads snarkjs + patches [fullProve](file:///Users/adityakumar/Library/Mobile%20Documents/com~apple~CloudDocs/monaris-app/src/lib/privacy/engine.ts#114-126) for RAILGUN compatibility |
| 2 | [usePrivateWallet.ts](file:///Users/adityakumar/Library/Mobile%20Documents/com~apple~CloudDocs/monaris-app/src/hooks/usePrivateWallet.ts#L123-L206) | [doInit()](file:///Users/adityakumar/Library/Mobile%20Documents/com~apple~CloudDocs/monaris-app/src/hooks/usePrivateWallet.ts#122-207) | Signs seed message, derives mnemonic, imports wallet |
| 3 | [engine.ts](file:///Users/adityakumar/Library/Mobile%20Documents/com~apple~CloudDocs/monaris-app/src/lib/privacy/engine.ts#L364-L446) | [doLoadProvider()](file:///Users/adityakumar/Library/Mobile%20Documents/com~apple~CloudDocs/monaris-app/src/lib/privacy/engine.ts#380-447) | Connects RPC, triggers quicksync with retries |
| 4 | [engine.ts](file:///Users/adityakumar/Library/Mobile%20Documents/com~apple~CloudDocs/monaris-app/src/lib/privacy/engine.ts#L482-L525) | [refreshPOIsForWallet()](file:///Users/adityakumar/Library/Mobile%20Documents/com~apple~CloudDocs/monaris-app/src/lib/privacy/engine.ts#482-526) | Generates POI proofs for pending UTXOs |

