## 9. Private Invoice Payment — Full Lifecycle

This is the complete flow when someone pays a Monaris invoice privately. It's orchestrated by [usePrivatePayment.ts](file:///Users/adityakumar/Library/Mobile%20Documents/com~apple~CloudDocs/monaris-app/src/hooks/usePrivatePayment.ts):

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Buyer as Buyer's Browser
    participant Hook as usePrivatePayment
    participant Wallet as usePrivateWallet
    participant Balance as usePrivateBalance
    participant TX as transactions.ts
    participant Privy as Privy SDK
    participant ARB as Arbitrum
    participant SB as Supabase

    Note over Buyer,SB: Step 1: Initialize
    Hook->>Wallet: Ensure private wallet exists
    Wallet-->>Hook: { walletId, railgunAddress, encryptionKey }

    Note over Buyer,SB: Step 2: Check Balance
    Hook->>Balance: Check privateUsdcBalance >= invoice amount
    alt Insufficient balance
        Hook-->>Buyer: ❌ "Shield more USDC first"
    end

    Note over Buyer,SB: Step 3: Resolve Recipient
    Hook->>SB: resolvePrivateAddress(sellerAddress, chainId)
    Note over SB: Look up seller's encrypted wallet blob
    Note over SB: If seller has RAILGUN wallet → return 0zk address
    Note over SB: If not → use buyer's own 0zk as escrow
    SB-->>Hook: recipientRailgunAddress: "0zk1q9..."

    Note over Buyer,SB: Step 4: Generate Proof (5-30 seconds)
    Hook->>TX: buildPrivateTransfer({ token, amount, recipient, memo })
    TX->>TX: Groth16 proof generation (see Section 8)
    TX-->>Hook: { success: true, transaction: { to, data } }

    Note over Buyer,SB: Step 5: Send Transaction
    Hook->>Privy: sendTransaction({ to, data, chainId })
    Privy->>ARB: Submit to Arbitrum
    ARB-->>Privy: txHash
    Privy-->>Hook: { hash: "0xabc..." }

    Note over Buyer,SB: Step 6: Record Receipt
    par Update Supabase (in parallel)
        Hook->>SB: INSERT private_receipts (payer, receiver, amount, tx_ref)
        Hook->>SB: UPDATE invoices SET payment_mode='PRIVATE', tx_ref=...
        Hook->>SB: INSERT notifications (seller, "Invoice Paid Privately")
    end

    Hook-->>Buyer: ✅ "Payment complete!"
    Hook->>Balance: refreshBalances()
```

### The 7 steps in code (annotated):

| Step | Status in UI | Code Reference | What happens |
|---|---|---|---|
| 1 | `initializing` | [usePrivatePayment.ts:69-74](file:///Users/adityakumar/Library/Mobile%20Documents/com~apple~CloudDocs/monaris-app/src/hooks/usePrivatePayment.ts#L69-L74) | Ensure RAILGUN wallet exists |
| 2 | `initializing` | [usePrivatePayment.ts:77-81](file:///Users/adityakumar/Library/Mobile%20Documents/com~apple~CloudDocs/monaris-app/src/hooks/usePrivatePayment.ts#L77-L81) | Check shielded USDC balance |
| 3 | `resolving` | [usePrivatePayment.ts:84-95](file:///Users/adityakumar/Library/Mobile%20Documents/com~apple~CloudDocs/monaris-app/src/hooks/usePrivatePayment.ts#L84-L95) | Look up seller's 0zk address from Supabase |
| 4 | `proving` | [usePrivatePayment.ts:98-114](file:///Users/adityakumar/Library/Mobile%20Documents/com~apple~CloudDocs/monaris-app/src/hooks/usePrivatePayment.ts#L98-L114) | **Groth16 proof generation** (the slow step) |
| 5 | `sending` | [usePrivatePayment.ts:119-133](file:///Users/adityakumar/Library/Mobile%20Documents/com~apple~CloudDocs/monaris-app/src/hooks/usePrivatePayment.ts#L119-L133) | Submit tx to Arbitrum via Privy |
| 6 | `recording` | [usePrivatePayment.ts:139-166](file:///Users/adityakumar/Library/Mobile%20Documents/com~apple~CloudDocs/monaris-app/src/hooks/usePrivatePayment.ts#L139-L166) | Record receipt + update invoice + notify seller |
| 7 | `done` | [usePrivatePayment.ts:169-171](file:///Users/adityakumar/Library/Mobile%20Documents/com~apple~CloudDocs/monaris-app/src/hooks/usePrivatePayment.ts#L169-L171) | Refresh balances, show success |

