## 10. Proof of Innocence (POI)

On Arbitrum (and Ethereum mainnet), RAILGUN requires **Proof of Innocence** — a mechanism to prevent sanctioned wallets from using the privacy system.

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    SHIELD["User Shields 100 USDC"] --> PENDING["Funds in ShieldPending bucket"]
    PENDING --> POI["POI Proof Generation"]
    POI --> SUBMIT["Submit POI to aggregator"]
    SUBMIT --> VERIFY["Aggregator verifies:<br/>- User is not on OFAC list<br/>- Funds are not from sanctioned source"]
    VERIFY -->|pass| SPEND["Funds move to Spendable bucket"]
    VERIFY -->|fail| STUCK["Funds stuck in MissingExternalPOI"]
```

### What happens in your code:

1. After shielding, funds land in **`ShieldPending`** bucket
2. [usePrivateWallet.ts:198-204](file:///Users/adityakumar/Library/Mobile%20Documents/com~apple~CloudDocs/monaris-app/src/hooks/usePrivateWallet.ts#L198-L204) calls [refreshPOIsForWallet()](file:///Users/adityakumar/Library/Mobile%20Documents/com~apple~CloudDocs/monaris-app/src/lib/privacy/engine.ts#482-526) during init
3. [usePrivateBalance.ts:169-203](file:///Users/adityakumar/Library/Mobile%20Documents/com~apple~CloudDocs/monaris-app/src/hooks/usePrivateBalance.ts#L169-L203) aggressively retries POI refresh every 15 seconds while `hasPendingFunds` is true
4. Once POI passes, funds move from `ShieldPending` → [Spendable](file:///Users/adityakumar/Library/Mobile%20Documents/com~apple~CloudDocs/monaris-app/src/lib/privacy/transactions.ts#467-535)

---

## 11. Balance Buckets

On POI-required networks (Arbitrum), shielded balances live in **buckets**:

```mermaid
graph LR
    subgraph "Balance Buckets"
        SP["Spendable<br/>Ready to use ✅"]
        SHP["ShieldPending<br/>Awaiting POI ⏳"]
        MIP["MissingInternalPOI<br/>Needs local proof ⚠️"]
        MEP["MissingExternalPOI<br/>Stuck — sanctioned? ❌"]
        SPENT["Spent<br/>Already consumed"]
    end
```

| Bucket | What it means | Can spend? |
|---|---|---|
| **Spendable** | POI passed, funds ready | ✅ Yes |
| **ShieldPending** | Just shielded, waiting for POI validation | ❌ No |
| **MissingInternalPOI** | Wallet needs to generate/submit POI proof | ❌ No (temporary) |
| **MissingExternalPOI** | External POI aggregator rejected or unreachable | ❌ No (contact support) |
| **Spent** | UTXO was consumed in a previous transaction | ❌ N/A |

Your code handles this in [usePrivateBalance.ts](file:///Users/adityakumar/Library/Mobile%20Documents/com~apple~CloudDocs/monaris-app/src/hooks/usePrivateBalance.ts):
- **`totalPrivateBalance`** = sum of ALL buckets except Spent
- **`totalSpendableBalance`** = only the Spendable bucket
- **`hasPendingFunds`** = `totalPrivateBalance > 0 && totalSpendableBalance < totalPrivateBalance`

---

## 12. Complete Architecture

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph "User's Browser"
        UI["React UI<br/>PrivatePayments.tsx<br/>ShieldDialog / UnshieldDialog"]
        HOOKS["React Hooks<br/>usePrivateWallet<br/>usePrivateBalance<br/>usePrivatePayment"]
        STORE["Zustand Store<br/>+ localStorage cache"]
        ENGINE["RAILGUN Engine<br/>(WASM binary)"]
        SNARK["snarkjs Prover<br/>(Groth16)"]
        IDB["IndexedDB<br/>- Merkle tree data<br/>- ZK circuit artifacts<br/>- WASM cache"]
    end

    subgraph "Supabase"
        WALLETS["user_private_wallets<br/>(encrypted blobs)"]
        RECEIPTS["private_receipts<br/>(payment records)"]
        INVOICES["invoices<br/>(payment_mode, tx_ref)"]
    end

    subgraph "Arbitrum"
        PROXY["RAILGUN Proxy<br/>0xFA709..."]
        MERKLE["Poseidon Merkle Tree<br/>(on-chain UTXOs)"]
        USDC["USDC Contract<br/>0xaf88d..."]
    end

    subgraph "External"
        IPFS["IPFS / HTTP<br/>ZK Circuit Artifacts<br/>(proving key, WASM)"]
        POI_AGG["POI Aggregator<br/>(Proof of Innocence)"]
        RPC["RPC Endpoints<br/>Ankr / dRPC / Alchemy"]
    end

    UI --> HOOKS
    HOOKS --> STORE
    HOOKS --> ENGINE
    ENGINE --> SNARK
    ENGINE --> IDB
    HOOKS --> WALLETS
    HOOKS --> RECEIPTS
    HOOKS --> INVOICES
    ENGINE --> RPC
    ENGINE --> MERKLE
    SNARK --> IPFS
    ENGINE --> POI_AGG
    PROXY --> MERKLE
    USDC --> PROXY
```

### Data flow summary:

| Data | Where it lives | Encrypted? |
|---|---|---|
| RAILGUN mnemonic | Supabase (encrypted blob) + derived on-the-fly from Privy signature | ✅ AES-256-GCM |
| RAILGUN wallet ID | Zustand store + localStorage | No (not sensitive) |
| RAILGUN 0zk address | Zustand store + localStorage | No (public equivalent) |
| Shielded balances | localStorage (cached) + live from Merkle tree | Cached values: no. On-chain: yes |
| Merkle tree data | IndexedDB + on-chain | On-chain: encrypted per-UTXO |
| ZK circuit artifacts | IndexedDB (cached from IPFS) | No (public circuits) |
| Proof of Innocence | Generated locally, submitted to aggregator | Proof is zero-knowledge |
| Private payment receipts | Supabase `private_receipts` table | Partial (encrypted_memo optional) |
